	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm developing a music engine for NES. What features, possibly missing from NT2 or MCK, would you like to see in the design? (This is a very open-ended question so that I can gather requirements from the community.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
